-- Bafokeng Holdings Agrees to Buy 5% Stake in RMB Holdings for $365 Million
-- B y   V e r n o n   W e s s e l s
-- 2010-12-15T09:41:52Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-12-15/bafokeng-holdings-agrees-to-buy-5-stake-in-rmb-holdings-for-365-million.html
Bafokeng Holdings Ltd. said it
agreed to buy a 5 percent interest in RMB Holdings Ltd. for 2.5
billion rand.  The company commented in an e-mailed statement today.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
